Active Surveillance Versus Watchful Waiting for Localized Prostate Cancer: A 
Model to Inform Decisions.

Loeb S(1), Zhou Q(2), Siebert U(3), Rochau U(4), Jahn B(4), Mühlberger N(4), 
Carter HB(5), Lepor H(6), Braithwaite RS(2).

