[Deaths and life expectancy losses attributable to diet high in sodium in 
China].

[Article in Chinese; Abstract available in Chinese from the publisher]

Liu SW(1), Cai Y(2), Zeng XY(1), Yin P(1), Qi JL(1), Liu YN(1), Liu JM(1), Zhao 
ZP(1), Zhang M(1), Wang LM(1), Wang LJ(1), Xue M(2), Zhou MG(1).

Author information:
(1)National Center for Chronic and Non-communicable Disease Control and 
Prevention, Chinese Center for Disease Control and Prevention, Beijing 100050, 
